{"lemma":"ضَرْبَةٌ","slug":"ضَرْبَةٌ","root":"ض.ر.ب","root_slug":"ض-ر-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-ر-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25700"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B6%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a blow, a stroke, a hit"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a shot, a report of a gun"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a punishment, a torment"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Instance noun from ضَرَبَ (ḍaraba, “to beat, hit”)."},"ipa":["/dˤar.ba/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25700","headword_ar":"ضَرْبَةٌ","root":"Drb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. n. un. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daraba","text_ar":"ضَرَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single act of beating, striking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.:"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a blow, stroke,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DarobN","text_ar":"ضَرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", fourth sentence. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DarobapF waAHidapF","text_ar":"ضَرْبَةً وَاحِدَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"At one time; once."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb.) So in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA A=xu*u maAliY Ealayoka A_il~aA DarobapF waAHidapF","text_ar":"لَا ا=خُذُ مَالِى عَلَيْكَ اـِلَّا ضَرْبَةً وَاحِدَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will not take what is due to me on thy part save at one time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"once"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Darobapu AlgaAy^iSi","text_ar":"ضَرْبَةُ الغَايِصِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is forbidden, is (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The saying of the diver for pearls, to the merchant, I will dive for thee once, and what I shall bring up shall be thine for such a price."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, Mgh, TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}